Once again, Gauteng leads the list of the Miss South Africa 2017 top 12 finalists with eight beauties representing the province, followed by KwaZulu-Natal and the Western Cape.The finalists, who were voted for by the general public through a newly introduced voting system, were unveiled at an exclusive ceremony in Sandton last night.Gauteng has better chances of success with Boipelo Mabe from Alexandra, Iman Mkwanazi from Lenasia, Nompumelelo Mampholo of Diepkloof, Benoni s Shan Naidoo, Shelbe Pretorius from Krugersdorp in the West Rand and three Pretoria beauties, Odirile Sepeng, Yuta Raubenheimer and Nicole van Niekerk.SIYABONGA SITHOLE